{
  "description_cn": "<p>负Z方向上的载荷，根据线的长度更新其大小。</p><p>根据直线的长短对直线端点施加向上的力。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 0, 0);\">权重</span>可以调节整体作用力大小的增大或减小。</p>",
  "description_en": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">A load in the negative Z direction, which updates its magnitude according to the length of the line</span></p><p>An upward force is applied to the endpoints of the line based on its length.\r\r</p><p>Weights can adjust the magnitude of the overall force by increasing or decreasing it.</p>",
